<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('./partials/head') %>
    <title>Workout</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-4bw+/aepP/YC94hEpVNVgiZdgIC5+VKNBQNGCHeKRQN+PtmoHDEXuppvnDJzQIu9" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <style>
        /* Add your custom styles here */
        body {
            background-image: url('/images/gym.png');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .hero {
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 0;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('./partials/nav') %>

    <div class="hero">
        <h1>Welcome to Your Workout Community</h1>
        <p>Where Fitness Meets Fun!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="container mt-4">
        <h1>Welcome to Workout Warriors!</h1>
        <p>We're not just a fitness website; we're a community of champions!</p>
        <p>At Workout Warriors, we believe in the power of fitness to transform lives. We're here to help you set new
            personal records, push your limits, and compete with fellow fitness enthusiasts from around the world.</p>
        <p>Our mission is simple: to inspire you, challenge you, and support you on your fitness journey. Whether you're
            a seasoned athlete or just starting out, you belong here.</p>
        <p>Join us today, and let's conquer new heights together!</p>
    </div>

    <%- include('./partials/scripts') %>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-HwwvtgBNo3bZJJLYd8oVXjrBZt8cqVSpeBNS5n7C8IVInixGAoxmnlMuBnhbgrkm" crossorigin="anonymous">
    </script>
</body>

</html>